Package: ssMRCT
Type: Package
Title: Regional consistency evaluation and sample size calculation for MRCTs
Version: 0.1.0 
Author: Kunhai Qing [cre, aut], Xinru Ren [aut], Jin Xu [aut]
Maintainer: Kunhai Qing <kunhaiq@qq.com>
Description: A comprehensive suite of functions for designing and analyzing Multi-Regional Clinical Trials (MRCTs) under fixed effects model and random effects model. It features sepcialized tools for consistency probability calculation and optimal regional fraction(s) determination. Support extends two MRCTs (two pivotal, independent MRCTs) under fixed effects model. Developed for regulatory decision support and trial optimization in global drug development programs.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: no
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: cubature, stats  
